{"tid":1689973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遍地開花轉做遍地開SHOP","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:11:22.000Z","uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d492f24c941e082680fda8d9b39c521628bf21","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"哨兵channel現時已經見到<br />\n旺角、黃大仙、沙田、老銅、荃灣有佈防<br />\n(應該係琴日手足話要五區遍地開花既位)<br />\n而抗爭將近五個月，大家都知道<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟戰</span>係要慢慢做，慢慢打。<br />\n將遍地開花呢樣野帶入去商場(講左好耐,但一直好似無乜人做)<br />\n一黎可以落閘，等的鋪頭被逼落閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二黎商場係較安全地方(唔排除又會衝入商場)<br />\n三黎話明係遍地，姐係係最近自己既大型商場到做，撤退較為安全<br />\n見到琴日咁多手足被警曱咬，成本同效益完全唔對等，何不做下較為和理方式繼續抗爭?<br />\n希望臨時吹雞可以吹入去和你SHOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩聽可以幫我呢個P牌仔推上去"},{"pid":"c18406e74e5f5ac189fbd1b7a8e57cd9a1e83b01","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7ccfe5a59b34c5f692202c538418bc736c30a91d","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"唔知吹唔吹到雞"},{"pid":"903dc740af371abfaf98c8247c1a16ee0db792ba","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"一係休息等警曱們哂太陽"},{"pid":"0084dda94091f1d4afa44adec22ab20e08520e00","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"一係SHOP一SHOP"},{"pid":"511c758636424478bfddc04563224996fc1e5bf6","tid":1689973,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"岩聽可以幫推唔岩聽等沉"},{"pid":"c31c266b54b652519af4862f87955acdb7c6729b","tid":1689973,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT